reviews.review_text: Cal Expo The weather was quite cool in Sacramento for this run and a couple of great shows resulted. Bobby opened with 1 More Sat Nite to open the Sunday show? Left a few of us  bewildered for a second or two. He must have forgot it the day before or something. Opening set was fun and highlighted by a China Cat>Rider ender. Second set included a Playin>UncleJohn>Playin>Miracle jam which was very well received. The Box of Rain encore was beautiful. One memory of the weekend was the volleyball court set up on the grass infield- great action before the show and during intermission.
